title: Henri Matisse Boxed Notecards
description:
Send your best wishes with the beautifully reproduced artwork on these full-color full size Notecard Boxes, packaged in a large format 2 piece glossy reusable box.

The work of Henri Matisse is reproduced in full color as notecards, including reproductions of 5 brilliant paintings. These museum quality boxed notecard sets are perfect to keep on hand for any occasion to send notes and greetings to friends and family.
  • Dimensions: 7.5 x 5.5 x 1.5 in.
  • Materials: 20 envelopes & 20 notecards, 5 each of 4 images
